專業助產士{{le|卡姆福特·莫莫|Comfort Momoh}}如此描述鎖陰手術：「年長女性和親友們會將女孩調整至{{le|膀胱切石臥位|Lithotomy position|切石臥位}}。之後她們會快速地深切兩側的陰蒂根部，直至[[小阴唇系带|小系帶]]。之後再使用剃刀直接切除大小陰唇。」<ref name=Momoh2005p7quote>[[Comfort_Momoh|Comfort Momoh]], "Female genital mutilation" in Comfort Momoh (ed.), ''Female Genital Mutilation'', Oxford: Radcliffe Publishing, 2005, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=dVjIP0RfVAMC&pg=PA7 7] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=dVjIP0RfVAMC&pg=PA7 |date=20160504121142 }}; also see [[Edna_Adan_Ismail|Edna Adan Ismail]], [http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf "Female genital mutilation survey in Somaliland"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf |date=20160402172434 }}, Edna Adan Maternity and Teaching Hospital, 2009, pp. 12–14.</ref>在索馬利亞，女孩的陰唇被切下之後，會被拿給年長女性，以確認手術是否完全<ref>[http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf Ismail 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf |date=20160402172434 }}, p. 12; also see Abusharaf 2007, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA190 190] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA190 |date=20170908222703 }}.</ref>。

確認之後，執刀者會在傷口中插入物品（如樹枝），為女性的陰部留下一個 2–3 mm 的開口，供經血和尿液排出{{efn|Jasmine Abdulcadira, ''Swiss Medical Weekly'', 2011:"In the case of infibulation, the urethral orifice and part of the vaginal opening are covered by the scar. In a virgin infibulated woman the small opening left for the menstrual fluid and the urine is not wider than 2–3 mm; in sexually active women and after the delivery the vaginal opening is wider but the urethral orifice is often still covered by the scar."<ref>[http://www.smw.ch/content/smw-2011-13137/ Abdulcadira et al. 2011] {{Wayback|url=http://www.smw.ch/content/smw-2011-13137/ |date=20160718085718 }}.</ref>}}<ref>For a twig, Momoh 2005, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=dVjIP0RfVAMC&pg=PA7 7] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=dVjIP0RfVAMC&pg=PA7 |date=20160504121142 }}.</ref>，並以手術用縫線（也可能是[[龍舌蘭屬|龍舌蘭]]或[[金合歡屬|金合歡屬]]植物的刺）縫合外陰。有些手術者會在傷口敷上藥膏，藥膏可能是以生蛋、藥草或是砂糖等調配而成<ref>[http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx Kelly and Hillard 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx |date=20170909054405 }}, p. 491; for the poultice, [http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf Ismail 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf |date=20160402172434 }}, p. 14.</ref><!--The parts that have been removed might be placed in a pouch for the girl to wear.<ref>El Guindi 2007, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA43 43].</ref>-->。為了幫助傷口癒合，女孩的雙腳會被綑綁起來（通常是從髖部綁到踝部）。綑綁的時間不一定，通常一周後會放鬆，兩周後會完全解開，有些則可能長達六周<ref>[http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx Kelly and Hillard 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx |date=20170909054405 }}, p. 491 (Kelly and Hillard say the girls are tied for 2–6 weeks); Momoh 2005, pp. [http://books.google.com/books?id=dVjIP0RfVAMC&pg=PA6 6–7] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=dVjIP0RfVAMC&pg=PA6 |date=20130921060154 }}; for progressive loosening of the binding, [http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf Ismail 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf |date=20160402172434 }}, p. 14.</ref>。<!--女性切除下來的部分會被裝在衣服上的一個口袋中，讓她隨身攜帶.。-->

專業助產士{{le|卡姆福特·莫莫|Comfort Momoh}} 亦曾如此描述：
<blockquote style="background:none; margin-right:5em; margin-left:0; border-left:solid 5px #ccc; padding:1.5em;">
（陰道開口處）是由鼓膜般的皮膚延伸覆蓋外陰處所餘之小孔。在執行切除的情況下，女孩多半會被牢牢固定住，但亦可能因劇烈掙扎，導致切口不受控制或雜亂無章；甚至可能因掙扎時用力過度而骨折或脫臼。<ref name=Momoh2005p7quote/></blockquote>

若女孩的家人認為鎖陰手術後留下的開口太大，會再進行鎖陰手術<ref>Abdalla 2007, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA190 190] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA190 |date=20170908222703 }}.</ref>。陰部的洞會在結婚後為了性交而開啟，第一次可能是助產士用小刀先割開，也有可能是她的先生直接用陰莖頂破。在包括索馬利蘭在內的一些國家，新郎及新娘的女性親友會觀看新娘陰部的開口，以確認她婚前未進行過性行為<ref>Abdalla 2007, pp. [http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA191 191], [http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA198 198] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA198 |date=20170908222903 }}; for the relatives, [http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf Ismail 2009] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ednahospital.org/female-genital-mutilation.pdf |date=20160402172434 }}, p. 14.</ref>。心理學家洪尼萊特富特 - 克萊因（Hanny Lightfoot-Klein）在1980年代採訪過上百對蘇丹的女性及男性，訪問有關接受鎖陰手術後的性行為：

<blockquote style="background:none; margin-right:5em; margin-left:0; border-left:solid 5px #ccc; padding:1.5em;">
若新娘已進行過鎖陰手術，新郎想直接用陰莖頂破鎖陰手術處，插入陰道進行性行為，以一般夫妻行房的頻率，約需要三至四天至數個月不等。有些男性因為鎖陰手術，完全無法進行陰道插入式性行為（在我的研究中，約佔15%），一般會由助產士進行手術切開，不過因為這反映男性的性能力較弱，因此會在非常秘密的情形下進行。有些無法進行插入式性行為的男性，即使在鎖陰手術的開口未打開的情形下，仍設法要讓妻子懷孕，若妻子懷孕了，其陰部的開口會切開以便分娩。有些（也許是所有）有這類情形的男性會用小刀協助打開妻子陰部的開口，過程中會疼痛，因為其陰部是漸漸撕裂越來越多，直到開口處可以讓陰莖插入為止。<ref>Hanny Lightfoot-Klein, [http://www.jstor.org/stable/3812643 "The Sexual Experience and Marital Adjustment of Genitally Circumcised and Infibulated Females in The Sudan"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jstor.org/stable/3812643 |date=20201004233951 }}, ''The Journal of Sex Research'', 26(3), 1989 (pp. 375–392), p. 380.<p>
Also see El Dareer 1982, pp. 42–49; Hanny Lightfoot-Klein, ''Prisoners of Ritual: An Odyssey Into Female Genital Circumcision in Africa'', New York: Routledge, 1989.</ref></blockquote>

<!--{{anchor|defibulation|deinfibulation|reinfibulation}}-->
女性在分娩時陰部被再次打開，分娩後再將之縫合，此過程稱為去縫陰手術和再縫陰手術。再縫陰手術包含再次剪開陰道來重建回第一次縫陰手術保留的那針孔大小的陰道口。此手術大約在婚前、分娩後、離婚和喪偶時執行{{efn|Elizabeth Kelly, Paula J. Adams Hillard, ''Current Opinion in Obstetrics & Gynecology'', 2005: "Women commonly undergo reinfibulation after a vaginal delivery. In addition to reinfibulation, many women in Sudan undergo a second type of re-suturing called El-Adel, which is performed to recreate the size of the vaginal orifice to be similar to the size created at the time of primary infibulation. Two small cuts are made around the vaginal orifice to expose new tissues to suture, and then sutures are placed to tighten the vaginal orifice and perineum. This procedure, also called re-circumcision, is primarily performed after vaginal delivery, but can also be performed before marriage, after cesarean section, after divorce, and sometimes even in elderly women as a preparation before death."<ref>[http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx Kelly and Hillard 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx |date=20170909054405 }}, p. 491.</ref>}}<ref>Asma El Dareer, ''Woman, Why Do You Weep: Circumcision and its Consequences'', London: Zed Press, 1982, pp. 56–64.<p>
Also see Rebecca J. Cooke, Bernard M. Dickens, [http://www.ijgo.org/article/S0020-7292%2810%2900045-7/abstract "Special commentary on the issue of reinfibulation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ijgo.org/article/S0020-7292%2810%2900045-7/abstract |date=20170101055347 }}, ''International Journal of Gynaecology and Obstetrics'', 109(2), May 2010, pp. 97–99. {{PMID|20178881}} {{doi|10.1016/j.ijgo.2010.01.004}}<p>
Gamal I. Serour, [http://www.ijgo.org/article/S0020-7292%2810%2900010-X/fulltext "The issue of reinfibulation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ijgo.org/article/S0020-7292%2810%2900010-X/fulltext |date=20170101055916 }}, ''International Journal of Gynaecology and Obstetrics'', 109(2), May 2010, pp. 93–96. {{PMID|20138274}} {{doi|10.1016/j.ijgo.2010.01.001}}<p>
Olukunmi O. Balogun, et al., [http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/enhanced/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD009872.pub2 "Interventions for improving outcomes for pregnant women who have experienced genital cutting"] {{Wayback|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/enhanced/doi/10.1002/14651858.CD009872.pub2 |date=20200410064039 }}, ''Cochrane Database of Systematic Reviews'', 2, 2013. {{PMID|23450610}} {{doi|10.1002/14651858.CD009872.pub2}}</ref>。

===第四型===
[[File:Intersex_individual_with_type_IIIb_circumcision.jpg|thumb]]
世界衛生組織定義第四型為「所有其他對女性外生殖器有害的的非醫療性行為」，包括刺入、刺穿、切割、刮除和燒灼。<ref name=WHO2014/>它包括切割陰核（象徵性的割禮）、燒灼或使陰部有疤痕，和植入物體到陰道使之更緊。<ref>[http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2008/9789241596442_eng.pdf WHO 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2008/9789241596442_eng.pdf |date=20130810080948 }}, p. 24; [http://www.unicef.org/media/files/FGCM_Lo_res.pdf UNICEF 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unicef.org/media/files/FGCM_Lo_res.pdf |date=20150405083031 }}, p. 7.</ref>{{le|陰唇牽拉|Labia stretching}}也歸類為第四類。<ref name=WHO2008p27>[http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2008/9789241596442_eng.pdf WHO 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://whqlibdoc.who.int/publications/2008/9789241596442_eng.pdf |date=20130810080948 }}, p. 27.</ref>常見於非洲南部和東部，此法是為了增強男性的性快感，而添加一種封閉空間感於女性。從八歲開始，就鼓勵女孩使用棍棒和按摩伸展其小陰唇。烏干達女孩被教育若無伸展陰唇則很難分娩。{{efn|WHO 2005: "In some areas (e.g. parts of Congo and mainland Tanzania), FGM entails the pulling of the labia minora and/or clitoris over a period of about 2 to 3 weeks. The procedure is initiated by an old woman designated for this task, who puts sticks of a special type in place to hold the stretched genital parts so that they do not revert back to their original size. The girl is instructed to pull her genitalia every day, to stretch them further, and to put additional sticks in to hold the stretched parts from time to time. This pulling procedure is repeated daily for a period of about two weeks, and usually no more than four sticks are used to hold the stretched parts, as further pulling and stretching would make the genital parts unacceptably long."<ref>[https://web.archive.org/web/20140428022806/http://www.who.int/gender/other_health/teachersguide.pdf "Female Genital Mutilation: A Teachers' Guide"], World Health Organization, 2005, p. 31.</ref>}}<ref>For the countries in which labia stretching is found (Botswana, Lesotho, Malawi, Mozambique, Namibia, South Africa, Tanzania, Uganda and Zimbabwe), see Nkiru Nzegwu, "'Osunality' (or African eroticism)" in Sylvia Tamale (ed.), ''African Sexualities: A Reader'', Cape Town: Fahamu/Pambazuka, 2011, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=xSqIrrswbG0C&pg=PA262 262].<p>
For the rest, Brigitte Bagnol and Esmeralda Mariano, "Politics of Naming Sexual Practices," in Tamale 2011, pp. [http://books.google.com/books?id=xSqIrrswbG0C&pg=PA272 272–276] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=xSqIrrswbG0C&pg=PA272 |date=20170908222903 }} (p. 272 for Uganda).</ref>

世界衛生組織在1995年針對女陰殘割的定義有包括在尼日及奈及利亞進行的{{le|吉西里切割|gishiri cutting}}{{efn|「''gishiri''」出自[[豪薩語|豪薩語]]，為「鹽」之意。}}（gishiri cutting）或安古利亞切割（angurya cutting）。因為有關其發生率及程序資訊的不足，世界衛生組織2008年的定義中已不包括這些方式<ref name=WHO2008p27/>。吉西里切割是為了處理不孕及難產等幾種問題，用刀片切割陰道前壁或後壁。在奈及利亞醫生馬里奧·烏斯曼·曼達拉（Mairo Usman Mandara）的研究中，進行過吉西里切割的女性，超過30%會有[[膀胱陰道瘺|膀胱陰道瘺]]的問題。安古利亞切割是將[[處女膜|處女膜]]切除，會在出生後第七天進行<ref name=Mandara2000p98>Mairo Usman Mandara, "Female genital cutting in Nigeria: View of Nigerian Doctors on the Medicalization Debate," in Bettina Shell-Duncan and Ylva Hernlund (eds.), ''Female "Circumcision" in Africa: Culture Controversy and Change'', Boulder: Lynne Rienner Publishers, 2000 (pp. 253–282), pp. [http://books.google.com/books?id=rhhRXiJIGEcC&pg=PA98 98] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=rhhRXiJIGEcC&pg=PA98 |date=20170908222903 }}, 100; for fistulae, p. 102.<p>
Mairo Usman Mandara, [http://www.ijgo.org/article/S0020-7292%2803%2900277-7/abstract "Female genital mutilation in Nigeria"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ijgo.org/article/S0020-7292%2803%2900277-7/abstract |date=20170101055213 }}, ''International Journal of Gynecology & Obstetrics'', 84(3), pp. 291–298. {{PMID|15001386}} {{doi|10.1016/j.ijgo.2003.06.001}}</ref>。

