女陰殘割對女性一生的身體及情緒健康都是有害的<ref name=Berg2014>Rigmor C. Berg, et al., [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4244458/ "Effects of female genital cutting on physical health outcomes: a systematic review and meta-analysis"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC4244458/ |date=20210308105220 }}, ''BMJ Open'', 4(11), 2014: e006316. {{PMID|25416059}} {{doi|10.1136/bmjopen-2014-006316}}</ref><ref name=RieselCreighton2015p49>Dan Reisel, Sarah M. Creighton, [http://www.maturitas.org/article/S0378-5122%2814%2900326-0/pdf "Long term health consequences of Female Genital Mutilation (FGM)"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.maturitas.org/article/S0378-5122%2814%2900326-0/pdf |date=20170101055716 }}, ''Maturitas'', 80(1), January 2015 (pp. 48–51), p. 49. {{PMID|25466303}} {{doi|10.1016/j.maturitas.2014.10.009}}</ref>，對於健康沒有任何已知的幫助<ref name=WHO2014health>[http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs241/en/ "Female genital mutilation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs241/en/ |date=20180402081316 }}, New York: World Health Organization, February 2014.</ref>
。其短期及後續的[[併發症|併發症]]和進行的女陰殘割種類，施行者是否有手術經驗，是否有用抗生素、用未消毒的手術器材或是醫療用的單次使用器材有關。若是進行鎖陰手術，後遺症的嚴重程度有許多影響因子，包含手術後所留下的孔穴大小、縫合是用手術用縫線還是植物的刺，以及程序是否進行不只一次（例如因為留下的孔穴太大而重新縫合，或是因為留下的孔穴太小而再開啟一個孔穴）等<ref name="Abdulcadira">Abdulcadira, Jasmine; Margairaz, C.; Boulvain, M; Irion, O. [http://www.smw.ch/content/smw-2011-13137/ "Care of women with female genital mutilation/cutting"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.smw.ch/content/smw-2011-13137/ |date=20160718085718 }}, ''Swiss Medical Weekly'', 6(14), January 2011 (review).</ref>。

手術後的常見併發症包括腫脹、出血過多、疼痛、[[尿滯留|尿滯留]]，或傷口感染。2015年的一份採集了56篇研究的回顧文章中提到，逾十分之一的女性在女陰殘割後發生了上述的併發症，其中的女陰殘割甚至包括象徵性的陰蒂切口（第四型），不過第三型的風險仍是最高的，報告也中認為此結果可能有低估<ref>Rigmor C. Berg, Vigdis Underland, [http://www.kunnskapssenteret.no/en/publications/immediate-health-consequences-of-female-genital-mutilation-cutting-fgm-c ''Immediate health consequences of female genital mutilation/cutting (FGM/C)''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kunnskapssenteret.no/en/publications/immediate-health-consequences-of-female-genital-mutilation-cutting-fgm-c |date=20150906001628 }}, ''Kunnskapssenteret'' (Norwegian Knowledge Centre for the Health Services), systematic review no. 8, 2014, pp. 4–5 ([http://www.kunnskapssenteret.no/en/publications/_attachment/166848?_ts=14853c40320&download=false full text] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kunnskapssenteret.no/en/publications/_attachment/166848?_ts=14853c40320&download=false |date=20161230003956 }}). ISBN 978-82-8121-856-7</ref>。其他短期症狀包括致命的大量出血、[[贫血|贫血]]、[[泌尿道感染|泌尿道感染]]、[[敗血症|敗血症]]、[[破傷風|破傷風]]、[[坏疽|坏疽]]、[[坏死性筋膜炎|坏死性筋膜炎]]（細菌將組織"吃掉"）及[[子宫内膜炎|子宫内膜炎]]<ref name=Abdulcadira/><ref name=RieselCreighton2015p49/><ref>Christos Iavazzo, Thalia A. Sardi, Ioannis D. Gkegkes, [http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs00404-012-2708-5 "Female genital mutilation and infections: a systematic review of the clinical evidence"] {{Wayback|url=http://link.springer.com/article/10.1007%2Fs00404-012-2708-5 |date=20201020102925 }}, ''Archives of Gynecology and Obstetrics'', 287(6), June 2013, pp. 1137–1149. {{PMID|23315098}} {{doi|10.1007/s00404-012-2708-5}}</ref>。因為這類的併發症可能沒有識別或是匯報，因此不確定有多少名女性因為這些併發症而死亡<ref>[http://www.unicef-irc.org/publications/pdf/fgm_eng.pdf UNICEF 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unicef-irc.org/publications/pdf/fgm_eng.pdf |date=20180928122738 }}, p. 16.</ref><ref name=RC2015p50>[http://www.maturitas.org/article/S0378-5122%2814%2900326-0/pdf Reisel and Creighton 2015] {{Wayback|url=http://www.maturitas.org/article/S0378-5122%2814%2900326-0/pdf |date=20170101055716 }}, p. 50.</ref>。手術者可能會用同一套器具為不同的人進行手術，這可能也會造成[[B型肝炎|B型肝炎]]、[[C型肝炎|C型肝炎]]及[[HIV|HIV]]的擴散，不過還沒有流行病學的研究可以證實這一點<ref name=RC2015p50/>。

後續的併發症因女陰割殘的類型不同而異<ref name=Abdulcadira/>。併發症包含導致難產的疤痕和[[蟹狀瘤|蟹狀瘤]]、受感染的[[表皮樣囊腫|表層狀囊包]]，也會影響陰蒂相關的{{le|神經增生|Neuroma}}<ref name=Kelly2005pp491-2/><ref>Amish J. Dave, Aisha Sethi, Aldo Morrone, [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0733863510001439 "Female Genital Mutilation: What Every American Dermatologist Needs to Know"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0733863510001439 |date=20150924173717 }}, ''Dermatologic Clinics'', 29(1), January 2011, pp. 103–109. {{PMID|21095534}} {{doi|10.1016/j.det.2010.09.002}}</ref>。受到陰戶縫合的女生可能會在陰戶留有2-3mm的孔洞，這個洞會造成[[排尿|解尿]]遲緩、滴尿、{{le|小便時疼痛|Dysuria}}，以及頻尿等症狀。尿液可能會在傷痕下聚積，造成皮膚底下長年潮濕，有可能會導致感染以及結石。有性行為或自然產的婦女在陰戶上會有較大的孔穴，但還是會因為傷痕組織而造成[[尿道|尿道]]開口受阻難產。可能會出現[[膀胱阴道瘘|膀胱阴道瘘]]或[[直腸陰道瘺|直腸陰道瘺]]（也就是阴道和尿道之間或是直腸和陰道之間有異常通道）<ref name=Abdulcadira/><ref name=Rushwan>Hamid Rushwan, [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1110570413000520 "Female genital mutilation: A tragedy for women's reproductive health"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1110570413000520 |date=20170118065735 }}, ''African Journal of Urology'', 19(3), September 2013, pp. 130–133. {{doi|10.1016/j.afju.2013.03.002}}</ref>。這些損害以及其他對尿道及膀胱的傷害可能會造成感染、[[尿失禁|尿失禁]]、[[性交疼痛|性交疼痛]]及[[不孕|不孕]]<ref name=Kelly2005pp491-2>[http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx Kelly and Hillard 2005] {{Wayback|url=http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2005/10000/Female_genital_mutilation.9.aspx |date=20170909054405 }}, pp. 491–492</ref>。

由於[[月經|月經]]期產生的經血淤塞、滯留在陰道和子宮而造成的[[痛經|痛經]]也很常見。如果陰道完全堵塞，會造成[[陰道積血|陰道積血]]或{{le|子宮積血|Hematometra}}<ref name=Abdulcadira/>。由於經血淤積造成的腹部腫脹和不來月經，使女孩看起來像是懷孕。雅斯瑪·艾爾·達理爾（Asma EI Dareer）醫生在1979年報告，一名有上述症狀的年輕蘇丹女孩被其家人所殺<ref>El Dareer 1982, p. 37. Also see Asma El Dareer, "Preliminary report on a study on prevalence and epidemiology of female circumcision in Sudan today," WHO seminar, Khartoum, 10–15 February 1979; Asma el Dareer, "Female circumcision and its consequences for mother and child," Yaounde, 12–15 December 1979, cited in [http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1110570413000520 Rushwan 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1110570413000520 |date=20170118065735 }}.</ref>。

