====北美====
加拿大於1994年7月授予來自索馬利亞的卡德拉·哈桑·法拉赫難民身份時，即認定女陰殘割是一種對女性的迫害<ref name=Farnsworth1994>Clyde H. Farnsworth, [http://www.nytimes.com/1994/07/21/world/canada-gives-somali-mother-refugee-status.html "Canada Gives Somali Mother Refugee Status"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1994/07/21/world/canada-gives-somali-mother-refugee-status.html |date=20170813224305 }}, ''The New York Times'', 21 July 1994.</ref>；卡德拉·哈桑·法拉赫在加拿大避難以避免她的女兒遭受女陰殘割之苦。加拿大政府於1997年修改{{le|加拿大刑法法典|Criminal Code of Canada}}268條法條中的部分法條，明令禁止女陰殘割，但若接受手術之人已滿18歲且沒有因此造成身體傷害則不在禁止範圍內<ref>[http://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/C-46/section-268.html Section 268] {{Wayback|url=http://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/acts/C-46/section-268.html |date=20190502191321 }}, Criminal Code; [http://www.unicef.org/media/files/FGCM_Lo_res.pdf UNICEF 2013] {{Wayback|url=http://www.unicef.org/media/files/FGCM_Lo_res.pdf |date=20150405083031 }}, p. 8.<p>
Also see Audrey Macklin, "The Double-Edged Sword: Using the Criminal Law Against Female Genital Mutilation," in Abusharaf 2007, p. [http://books.google.com/books?id=8VQxt634pfcC&pg=PA211 211ff]; [http://sogc.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/gui299CPG1311E.pdf "Female Genital Cutting"] {{Wayback|url=http://sogc.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/gui299CPG1311E.pdf |date=20160115090558 }}, Clinical practice guidelines, No. 299, The Society of Obstetricians and Gynaecologists of Canada, November 2013.</ref>。截止至2015年2月，仍未有針對女陰殘割的訴訟<ref>Also see Mobina S. B. Jaffer, [http://www.parl.gc.ca/Content/Sen/Chamber/411/Debates/079db_2012-05-15-e.htm "Criminal Code, Bill to Amend – Second Reading] {{Wayback|url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/Content/Sen/Chamber/411/Debates/079db_2012-05-15-e.htm |date=20160728022949 }}, Debates of the Senate (Hansard), 1st Session, 41st Parliament, 148(79), 15 May 2012.</ref>。

